Learn secrets and historical facts about the world around you.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 知识利器，满足你的好奇心

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: “What’s that building?” “Which movie do I recognize this street from?” “Is there anything interesting to see around here?” By pulling in relevant nearby information from Wikipedia, Inquire can answer all sorts of questions. Whether you’re on vacation, have a spare half-hour while visiting an unfamiliar city, or just want to discover new things in your hometown, Inquire is the perfect pocket companion for curious minds.
